Package org.axiondb.engine

Core database machinery.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
ArrayIndexFactory An IndexFactory for array indices.
AxionColumnsMetaTableUpdater Updates the AXION_TABLES meta table
AxionSequencesMetaTableUpdater Updates the AXION_SEQUENCES meta table
AxionTablesMetaTableUpdater Updates the AXION_TABLES meta table
AxionTypesMetaTableUpdater Updates the AXION_TYPES meta table
BaseArrayIndex Abstract base implemenation for indices that maintain an in-memory, sorted array of key values (and their associated row identifiers).
BaseBTreeIndex Abstract base implementation for B-Tree based indices.
BaseDatabase Abstract base Database implementation.
BaseDiskTable Abstract base disk-resident implementation of Table.
BaseIndex Abstract base implementation of Index.
BaseRow An abstract base implementation of Row, providing equals, hashCode and toString implementations.
BaseTable An abstract base implementation of Table.
BaseWhereNodeVisitor A WhereNodeVisitor that delegates incoming WhereNodes to the appropriate method.
BTreeIndexFactory An IndexFactory for B-Tree indices.
ClearBindVariableWhereNodeVisitor A WhereNodeVisitor that clears any BindVariables found in the tree.
Databases A static Map of Databases by name.
DiskDatabase A disk-resident Database.
DiskSystemTable A disk-resident Table in plain-text format.
DiskTable A disk-resident Table.
DiskTableFactory A TableFactory for disk-based tables.
FindBindVariableWhereNodeVisitor Deprecated. Apparently no longer used (replaced by CollectBindVariableWhereNodeVisitor)
FlattenWhereNodeVisitor Decomposes a WhereNode tree into a HashSet of WhereNodes that were originally ANDed together in the source tree.
IntArrayIndex An array index over integer keys.
IntArrayIndexLoader An IndexLoader for IntArrayIndex.
IntBTreeIndex A B-Tree index over integer keys.
IntBTreeIndexLoader An IndexLoader for IntBTreeIndex.
LazyRow A Row which loads data from a RowSource as needed.
MemoryDatabase A memory-resident Database.
MemoryTable A memory-resident Table.
MemoryTableFactory A TableFactory for memory-based tables.
ObjectArrayIndex An index over Object keys.
ObjectArrayIndexLoader An IndexLoader for ObjectArrayIndex.
ObjectBTreeIndex A B-Tree index over Object keys.
ObjectBTreeIndexLoader An IndexLoader for ObjectBTreeIndex.
ReferencesOtherTablesWhereNodeVisitor Return true if reference a table other than the given one, false otherwise.
SimpleRow A simple implementation of Row.
SnapshotIsolationTransaction A Transaction implementation that provides "snapshot isolation", which supports TRANSACTION_SERIALIZABLE isolation without locking.
SortedMapIndex An Index based upon a SortedMap.
SortedMapIndexLoader An IndexLoader for SortedMapIndex.
TransactableTableImpl An implemenation of TransactableTable.
TransactionManagerImpl An implemenation of TransactionManager currently only supportd SnapshotIsolationTransactions.
